 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uragtooth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ragtooth</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 137<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 9:35:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What to upgrade next?</span><hr size=1> A magelo profile link would be handy <p>Ragtooth Irongrip <br>
