</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukaldanm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kaldanm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 10:00:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Upgrade</span><hr size=1> First, use your frosty as Primary weapon. The proc aggro better. <br>
<br>
And complete warlord armor <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugedes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gedes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 10:06:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Upgrade</span><hr size=1> Depending on the situation, I use my frosty in my main hand.  Sometimes I use it in off to prevent stealing aggro if I am not main tank (and I gotta tell ya, I don't get aggro worth a damn anymore). <p><a
href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2372"><Br>Thor<Br>Lost Myrmidon</a><Br><Br><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/c_warrior.gif"border="0"<Br><Br><Br>"It's never too late to be what you might have been - George Eliot"
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ufatsdomino86.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FatsDomino86</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 10:25:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   weapons...</span><hr size=1> In my expirience, the best investment I've made to date was in a Wavecrasher...9/19, some jumbled stats, and an UBER taunt. If aggro control is your issue, a WC will fix that, trust me. If my proc goes off on a mob I'm not MTing, then I become the MT right away. Not to mention the proc is nice when you dont have a shammy or enc for slows...<br>
<br>
Just my 2cp<br>
<br>
Razzo, Ogre Champion of the 52nd<br>
Lost Collective <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uragtooth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ragtooth</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 12:27:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: weapons...</span><hr size=1> Haste?<br>
<br>
