<br>
Otherwise Ornate sword is a bit better over the lammy ...and it wont hit your 20K reserve.  <br>
<br>
 <p>Ragtooth Irongrip <br>
40 Warrior <br>
The Guard<br>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=255210> My Profile </a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugedes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gedes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 12:52:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: weapons...</span><hr size=1> Well, thanks for the great advised guys!<br>
I will certainly look into the WaveCrasher, I don't if it take's all my 20k to do it, as long as I can hold taunt better. haha<br>
<br>
As for haste, I don't like haste items if I have to sacrifice other things to get it.  I have a 60 Sham that I group with 100% of the time I play, so that is my haste item. lol<br>
Aside from that I think I'll wait for a haste earring or ring of some sort.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a
href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2372"><Br>Thor<Br>Lost Myrmidon</a><Br><Br><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/c_warrior.gif"border="0"<Br><Br><Br>"It's never too late to be what you might have been - George Eliot"
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ualderianstormguarddr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alderian Stormguard DR</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/2/02 7:30:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~thoennep/aldwerewolf.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: weapons...</span><hr size=1> Cougar Claw Earring<br>
Mushroom Veil<br>
Spider Fur Collar<br>
<br>
All have to go.  Get a clattering bone necklace, earring of the solstice, and maybe crystal spider eyes.<br>
<br>
Depending on the amount of haste, the extra DPS can really make up for the not so great stats, especially for tauntage.  But it's your character, do what you feel is best.<br>
<br>
Just a thought. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=96181" target="blank">Alderian Stormguard</a><BR>
Warlord of KoWP</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utaminy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taminy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/4/02 12:32:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Haste...</span><hr size=1> You need a haste item; they stack with haste spells, and 20-30% haste from a low or mid end haste item is a lot of damage you're giving up for a few stats. FBSS and Sash of the Dragonborn are IMO the best value you for your hard earned plat. Either of these would leave you plenty of money to upgrade your other items (unless your server's prices are much different than mine). If you want to simply get the best haste item you can afford, try to get an RBG (may be a little out of your price range, depending how much they go for on your server and if you can sell your current belt).<br>
<br>
Most of the other upgrades you can go with are fairly cheap:<br>
<br>
Ears: Electrum Black Sapphire (2ac 35hp) and/or Earring of the Solstice (I can get these for just under 5k going through the people with trade skills in my alliance).<br>
<br>
Face: Crystal Spider Eyes or Enshrouded Veil<br>
<br>
Necklace: Clattering Bone Necklace was mentioned... but since you appear to be on giant faction, I reccomend a Collar of the Storm. It's a very easy quest if you know someone with Tower of Frozen Shadow keys. Clattering Bone Necklace is good too if you don't want to do the quest though.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/u1ludor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>1Ludor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/4/02 1:16:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Haste...</span><hr size=1> the haste stacks, nothing is even close to as important as getting a haste item of some kind. fbss alone would do wonders for your damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uvelyssa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Velyssa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 128<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/4/02 12:30:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4060.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Haste...</span><hr size=1> WC will likely eat your cash reserve and be looking for more, if your server is like mine.<br>
